metadata.description:
Techno remix of Natasha Bedingfield's "Unwritten", remixed by DJ エリ君

Finished and released May 25th, 2015. Incl. "Unwritten (Michael Nigro & Johnny Vicious Warehouse Mix)": Natasha Bedingfield, "Unwritten (Acoustic Version)": Natasha Bedingfield. Art: unknown creator.
